## Responsive Design

### Tablet (< 900px)

```css
@media (max-width: 900px) {
    .typography {
        max-width: 100%;
        padding: 0 1rem;
    }
}
```

### Mobile (< 768px)

```css
@media (max-width: 768px) {
    article h1 {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
    article h2 {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
    }
}
```

## Customizing

### Adding New Colors

```css
:root {
    --{{ css_prefix }}-success: #10b981;
    --{{ css_prefix }}-success-light: #d1fae5;
}

.dark {
    --{{ css_prefix }}-success-light: #065f46;
}
```

### Overriding Theme Defaults

Use `!important` sparingly to override shadcn defaults:

```css
article a {
    color: var(--{{ css_prefix }}-primary) !important;
}
```

Use existing variables for consistency throughout your customizations.
